\c 14
\s Iqhinga lokumbulala uJesu
\p
\v 1 Kwathi emva kwensuku ezimbili kwaba khona iphasika l\add omkhosi \add*wesinkwa esingelamvubelo; abapristi abakhulu lababhali basebedinga ukuthi bangambamba njani ngobuqili ba\add m\add*bulale;
\v 2 kodwa bathi: Kungabi ngomkhosi, hlezi kube lesiphithiphithi sabantu\x + 14.1,2, Mat. 26.2-5. Luka 22.1,2.\x*.
\s UJesu uyagcotshwa eBethani
\p
\v 3 Kwathi eseBethani, endlini kaSimoni umlephero, ehlezi ekudleni, kwafika owesifazana ephethe umfuma \w we-alibasta\w** wamagcobo \w awenadi\w** uqobo aligugu elikhulu; wasephahlaza umfuma we-alibasta, wa\add wa\add*thela ekhanda lakhe.
\v 4 Kwakukhona abanye abathukuthelayo ngaphakathi kwabo, besithi: Kwenzelwani ukumotshwa kwalamagcobo?
\v 5 Ngoba la abengathengiswa \add ngemali\add* edlula \w odenariyo\w** abangamakhulu amathathu, besekunikwa abayanga. Basebemsola.
\v 6 Kodwa uJesu wathi: Myekeleni; limhluphelani? Wenze umsebenzi omuhle kimi.
\v 7 Ngoba abayanga lihlala lilabo, futhi uba lithanda lingabenzela okuhle; kodwa mina kalihlali lilami\x + Mat. 26.6-13. Joha. 12.1-8.\x*.
\v 8 Yena wenzile abengakwenza; uqalile ngaphambili ukuwugcobela ukungcwatshwa umzimba wami\x + Mat. 26.12.\x*.
\v 9 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Loba ngaphi emhlabeni wonke lapho okuzatshunyayelwa khona lelivangeli, lalokhu akwenzileyo kuzakhulunywa ngakho kube yisikhumbuzo ngaye.
\s Umvuzo wokumnikela uJesu
\p
\v 10 UJudasi Iskariyothi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili, wasesiya kubapristi abakhulu, ukuze amnikele kubo\x + 14.10,11, Mat. 26.14-16. Luka 22.3-6. Joha. 13.2,27,30.\x*.
\v 11 Futhi sebezwile bathokoza, bathembisa ukumnika imali; wasedinga ukuthi angamnikela njani kuhle\x + 2 Tim. 4.2. Mat. 26.16. Luka 22.6.\x*.
\s Ukumiswa kwesidlo esingcwele
\p
\v 12 Kwathi ngosuku lokuqala lwesinkwa esingelamvubelo, ababehlaba ngalo iphasika, abafundi bakhe bathi kuye: Uthanda ukuthi siyelungisa ngaphi ukuze udle iphasika\x + Mat. 26.17-19. Luka 22.7-13.\x*?
\v 13 Wasethuma ababili kubafundi bakhe\x + Luka 22.8.\x*, wathi kubo: Hambani liye emzini, njalo umuntu uzahlangana lani ethwele imbiza yamanzi; limlandele,
\v 14 njalo loba kungaphi azangena khona, kalibokuthi kumninindlu: UMfundisi uthi: Ingaphi indlu yezihambi, lapho engingadlela khona iphasika labafundi bami\x + Luka 2.7.\x*?
\v 15 Futhi yena uzalitshengisa indlu enkulu ephezulu eyendlelweyo elungisiweyo; silungiseleni khona.
\v 16 Abafundi bakhe basebephuma, bangena emzini, bathola kunjengokutsho kwakhe kubo; basebelungisa iphasika.
\p
\v 17 Kwathi sekukusihlwa wafika labalitshumi lambili.
\v 18 Sebehlezi besidla, uJesu wathi: Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Omunye wenu, odla lami, uzanginikela\x + Mat. 26.20-24.\x*.
\v 19 Basebeqala ukudabuka, bathi kuye ngamunye ngamunye: Ayisimi, akunjalo yini? Lomunye: Ayisimi, akunjalo yini\x + Joha. 8.9.\x*?
\v 20 Kodwa waphendula wathi kubo: \add Ng\add*omunye wabalitshumi lambili, otsheba kanye lami emganwini.
\v 21 Sibili iNdodana yomuntu ihamba, njengokulotshiweyo ngayo; kodwa maye kulowomuntu enikelwa nguye iNdodana yomuntu! Bekungakuhle kuye aluba lowomuntu wayengazalwanga.
\p
\v 22 Kwathi besidla, uJesu wathatha isinkwa, wa\add si\add*busisa wa\add si\add*hlephula, wabanika, wathi: Thathani, lidle; lokhu kungumzimba wami.
\v 23 Wasethatha inkezo, esebongile wabanika; basebenatha kuyo bonke.
\v 24 Wasesithi kubo: Leli ligazi lami, elesivumelwano esitsha, elichithelwa abanengi\x + Mat. 26.26-29. Luka 22.19,20. 1 Kor. 11.23-25.\x*.
\v 25 Ngiqinisile ngithi kini: Angisayikunatha okwesithelo sevini, kuze \add kufike\add* lolosuku engizasinatha ngalo sisitsha embusweni kaNkulunkulu.
\v 26 Kwathi sebehlabele ingoma yokudumisa baphuma baya entabeni yeMihlwathi.
\s Ukuxwayiswa kukaPetro
\p
\v 27 UJesu wasesithi kubo: Lonke lizakhubeka ngami ngalobubusuku; ngoba kulotshiwe \add ukuthi\add*: Ngizatshaya umelusi, izimvu besezihlakazeka\x + Zek. 13.7.\x*.
\v 28 Kodwa emva kokuvuswa kwami, ngizalandulela ukuya eGalili.
\v 29 Kodwa uPetro wathi kuye: Lanxa bonke bezakhubeka, kodwa hatshi mina\x + Joha. 21.15.\x*.
\v 30 UJesu wasesithi kuye: Ngiqinisile ngithi kuwe: Lamuhla ngalobubusuku, lingakakhali kabili iqhude, uzangiphika kathathu\x + 14.68,72. Mat. 26.34,75. Luka 22.34,60. Joha. 13.38; 18.27.\x*.
\v 31 Kodwa waqinisa ngamandla esithi: Loba kudingeka ngife lawe, angisoze ngikuphike. Basebesitsho njalo labo bonke.
\s EGetsemane
\p
\v 32 Basebefika endaweni ebizo layo yiGetsemane; wasesithi kubafundi bakhe: Hlalani phansi lapha, ngisa\add ya\add*khuleka\x + Mat. 26.36-46. Luka 22.39-42,45,46.\x*.
\v 33 Wasethatha kanye laye uPetro loJakobe loJohane, waseqala ukudatshulwa sibili lokukhathazeka kakhulu.
\v 34 Wasesithi kubo: Umphefumulo wami udabukile kakhulu kuze kube sekufeni; hlalani lapha lilinde\x + 9.15.\x*.
\v 35 Waseqhubeka ibangana, wawela emhlabathini, wakhuleka ukuthi, uba kungenzeka, kudlule kuye lelihola\x + Joha. 12.27; 13.1. Mark. 14.41. Luka 22.53.\x*.
\v 36 Wasesithi: \w Abha\w**, Baba\x + Roma 8.15. Gal. 4.6.\x*, zonke izinto ziyenzeka kuwe. Susa linkezo kimi\x + Mat. 19.26. Heb. 5.7.\x*; kodwa kungabi yikuthi ngithandani mina, kodwa kube yikuthi \add uthanda\add*ni wena\x + Mat. 19.26. Heb. 5.7.\x*.
\v 37 Wasesiza, wabafica belele, wathi kuPetro: Simoni, ulele yini? Ubungelinde yini ihola libe linye?
\v 38 Lindani likhuleke, ukuze lingangeni ekulingweni. Umoya uyavuma-ke, kodwa inyama ibuthakathaka.
\v 39 Wasebuya wahamba wa\add ya\add*khuleka, esitsho wona lawomazwi\x + Mat. 26.39,42.\x*.
\v 40 Wasebuya wabafica futhi belele; ngoba amehlo abo ayenzima, kodwa babengazi ukuthi bazamphendula \add bathi\add*ni\x + 9.6.\x*.
\v 41 Wasesiza ngokwesithathu, wathi kubo: Qhubekani-ke lilele, liphumule. Kwanele; ihola selifikile; khangelani, iNdodana yomuntu iyanikelwa ezandleni zezoni.
\v 42 Sukumani, sihambe; khangelani, onginikelayo useduze\x + Joha. 13.1.\x*.
\s Ukubotshwa kukaJesu lokuthethwa kwecala lakhe
\p
\v 43 Kwathi esakhuluma, wahle wafika uJudasi, omunye wabalitshumi lambili, njalo elexuku elikhulu elilezinkemba lezinduku, livela kubapristi abakhulu lababhali labadala.
\v 44 Lomnikelayo wayebanike isiboniso, esithi: Lowo engizamanga, nguye; limbambe, li\add m\add*qhube li\add m\add*qinise.
\v 45 Esefikile, wahle wasondela kuye wathi: \w Rabi\w**, Rabi! Wasemanga.
\v 46 Basebemdumela, bambamba.
\v 47 Lomunye kwababemi khona wakhokha inkemba wagadla inceku yompristi omkhulu, waquma indlebe yayo.
\p
\v 48 UJesu wasephendula wathi kubo: Liphume njengokuyamelana lomphangi yini lilezinkemba lezinduku ukuzangibamba?
\v 49 Bengilani insuku ngensuku ethempelini ngifundisa, kodwa kalingibambanga - kodwa ukuze kugcwaliseke imibhalo\x + Mat. 26.47-56. Luka 22.47-53. Joha. 18.3-11.\x*.
\v 50 Bonke basebemtshiya babaleka.
\v 51 Lejaha elithile lamlandela, lembethe ilembu elicolekileyo \add emzimbeni\add* onqunu. Aselibamba amajaha\x + 2 Sam. 4.12.\x*;
\v 52 laselitshiya ilembu elicolekileyo lababalekela linqunu.
\s UJesu uphambi kompristi omkhulu
\p
\v 53 Basebemqhuba uJesu \add bamusa\add* kumpristi omkhulu; basebebuthana kuye abapristi abakhulu bonke labadala lababhali\x + 14.61-65, Luka 22.54. Mat. 26.57-68. Joha. 18.12-15. Joha. 18.19-24. Luka 22.63-65. Luka 22.67-69.\x*.
\v 54 UPetro wasemlandela ekhatshana waze waba phakathi kweguma lompristi omkhulu; wayehlezi kanye lezinceku, esotha umlilo\x + 14.67. Joha. 18.18,25.\x*.
\p
\v 55 Labapristi abakhulu lomphakathi wonke badinga ubufakazi ngoJesu, ukuze bambulale; kodwa kababutholanga.
\v 56 Ngoba abanengi bafakaza amanga ngaye, kodwa lobubufakazi kabuvumelananga\x + 14.59.\x*.
\v 57 Kwasekusukuma abanye bafakaza amanga amelana laye besithi:
\v 58 Thina samuzwa esithi: Mina ngizadiliza lelithempeli\x + 15.29.\x* elenziwe ngezandla\x + Seb. 7.48; 17.24. Heb. 9.11,24.\x*, njalo ngakhe elinye elingenziwanga ngezandla\x + 2 Kor. 5.1.\x* ngensuku ezintathu.
\v 59 Loba kunjalo ubufakazi babo kabuvumelananga\x + 14.59.\x*.
\v 60 Kwasekusukuma umpristi omkhulu phakathi \add kwabo\add* wambuza uJesu, esithi: Kawuphenduli lutho yini? Bafakazani laba okumelana lawe?
\v 61 Kodwa wathula, kaphendulanga lutho. Umpristi omkhulu wabuya wambuza, wathi kuye: Wena unguKristu, iNdodana yoBusisiweyo yini?
\v 62 UJesu wasesithi: Mina nginguye. Njalo lizabona iNdodana yomuntu ihlezi ngakwesokunene samandla, isiza ngamayezi ezulu\x + Mat. 24.30.\x*.
\v 63 Umpristi omkhulu wasedabula izembatho zakhe wathi: Sisaswelelani abafakazi?
\v 64 Liyizwile inhlamba; licabangani? Bonke basebemlahla ukuthi ulecala lokufa.
\p
\v 65 Abanye basebeqala ukumkhafulela amathe, lokumgubuzela ubuso, lokumdutshuza\x + Esta 7.8. Luka 22.64.\x*, lokuthi kuye: Profetha\x + Mat. 26.28. Luka 22.64.\x*! Izinceku zasezimwakala\x + Mat. 26.67.\x*.
\s UPetro ulandula uJesu
\p
\v 66 UPetro esegumeni ngaphansi\x + Mat. 26.69-75. Luka 22.55-62. Joha. 18.16-18. Joha. 18.25-27.\x*, kwafika enye yezincekukazi zompristi omkhulu\x + 14.54. Joha. 18.17.\x*;
\v 67 isibona uPetro esotha, yamkhangela yathi: Lawe ubulomNazaretha, uJesu\x + 14.54.\x*.
\v 68 Kodwa waphika, wathi: Kangikwazi, futhi kangikuqedisisi okutshoyo. Wasephuma phandle, waya entubeni; laselikhala iqhude\x + 14.30.\x*.
\p
\v 69 Njalo incekukazi encane yabuya yambona, yaqala ukutsho kwababemi khona \add ukuthi\add*: Lo ungo\add munye\add* wabo\x + Mat. 26.71.\x*.
\v 70 Kodwa wabuya waphika. Kwathi emva kwesikhatshana futhi labo ababemi khona bathi kuPetro: Ngeqiniso ungo\add munye\add* wabo; ngoba lawe ungumGalili\x + Luka 22.59.\x*, lolimi lwakho luyavumelana\x + Seb. 2.7.\x*.
\v 71 Waseqala ukuqalekisa lokufunga esithi: Kangimazi lumuntu elimtshoyo.
\v 72 Iqhude laselikhala ngokwesibili. UPetro wasekhumbula ilizwi uJesu ayelitshilo kuye lokuthi: Lingakakhali kabili iqhude, uzangiphika kathathu\x + 14.30.\x*. Esenakane ngalokhu wakhala.